description: "A plan of a bakery in an unknown location in the Dutch East Indies, next to a proposed water channel (‘rijool’) intended to power a saw mill. There are two additional sheets showing construction drawings of the water channel, with piling underneath."
title: "Plan van de nieuw aangelegde bakkerij, gelegen beweste de zaahmool, dienende tot aanwijzing op welke manier de rijool, dienen gemaakt te worden in het jaar ao 1813"
